  "instructions": [
    "Cut the firm tofu into small cubes.",
    "In a blender or food processor, combine Branston pickle, soy sauce, apple cider vinegar, minced garlic, smoked paprika, and miso paste. Blend until smooth.",
    "Transfer the marinade to a shallow dish and add the tofu cubes. Mix well to coat the tofu evenly.",
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the tofu and cook for 3-4 minutes on each side, until lightly browned and crispy.",
    "Transfer the cooked tofu to a plate and top with chopped green onions.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
